che16.dcs.aber.ac.uk.model

Class AntColonyOptimisation

  • java.lang.Object
    • java.util.Observable
      • che16.dcs.aber.ac.uk.model.AntColonyOptimisation

  • public class AntColonyOptimisation
extends java.util.Observable
    This Class is the main data centre for the underlying Ant Colony algorithms present in this application. This Class is also the entry point for the che16.dcs.aber.ac.uk.model package. This Class contains the relevant parameter values and World instance required for algorithm execution.
    Author:
    Christopher Edwards

        Used to progress the algorithms step based execution by one step. This is only used if the application is in step-based iteration mode otherwise start() is used.
